Key%29>e vedere anche <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> e <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="910c2-167">See the example for <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.Append%28System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey%29>, and also see <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>.</span></span>  
  
