-   <xref:System.String>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="910c2-468">Questo metodo accetta gli oggetti elencati in precedenza per il `builder` parametro.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="910c2-468">This method accepts the objects listed above for the `builder` parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="910c2-469">Per altre informazioni, vedere il <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> operatori.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="910c2-469">For more information, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> operators.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="910c2-470">È il metodo equivalente per l'operatore <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.Add%28System.String%2CSystem.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder%29?displayProperty=nameWithType></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="910c2-470">The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.Add%28System.String%2CSystem.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder%29?displayProperty=nameWithType></span></span>  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="910c2-471">L'esempio seguente crea una grammatica di riconoscimento vocale in grado di riconoscere le due frasi, "sfondo *colore*" e "impostata in background *colore*", dove *colore* viene selezionato da un set di colori.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="910c2-471">The following example creates a speech recognition grammar that can recognize the two phrases, "Make background *color*" and "Set background to *color*", where *color* is selected from a set of colors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="910c2-472">Diversi tipi utilizzati per compilare la grammatica finale, ad esempio [stringa](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159733), <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>, e <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> oggetti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="910c2-472">Various types are used to build the final grammar, such as [String](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159733), <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects.</span></span>  
  
